Interface DomainProducer

All Known Implementing Classes:
Chull, Circle, Rect
public interface DomainProducer

Classes which inplement this interface should be able to produce domains which can be used in intersection. IN some cases it will be easier to simply get a domain for shape - even if perhaps that domain contains only a single convex. MOst geometric shapes will implement this and ConvexProducer.
